Package com.vtls.opensource.formats

Interface Summary
FormatProperties This interface provides the property names and functions for Property extended classes representing the useful information for files in different formats.
 

Class Summary
AudioProperties This class is a collection of properties for a valid Audio file.
FormatPropertiesFactory Usage: FormatPropertiesFactory source_factory = FormatPropertiesFactory.getInstance(); ImageSource source = source_factory.getProperties("text/plain", (InputStream)stream);
ImageProperties This class is a collection of properties for a valid Image file.
JPEG2000Properties This class is a collection of properties for a file of a valid JPEG 2000 codestream.
JPEGProperties This class is a collection of properties for a valid JPEG file.
MediaProperties This class is a collection of properties for Media files, i.e., video and audio files.
MicrosoftDocumentProperties This class is a collection of properties for Microsoft Document files.
MrSIDProperties This class is a collection of properties for a MrSID file.
PDFProperties This class is a collection of properties for a PDF file.
XMLProperties This class is a collection of properties for an XML file.
